Title: A Whelping Hand
Description:
Well done, $n.

Now we must ensure the whelps of the netherwing have the best opportunities to grow and flourish. 

Let us speak to Mother Elion. I know she would relish the opportunity to care for the young of a new flight. 

Can you meet us at the Ruby Lifeshrine?
ObjectivesText: Meet Mother Elion at the Ruby Lifeshrine in the Waking Shores.
